de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.pcmconnection

Class PcmNameParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.pcmconnection.PcmNameParser

  • public class PcmNameParser
extends Object
    ****************************EXTINCT**************************************************** ******** This parser is a draft that can only provide proper functionality if SoMoX does not change its naming convention for EntityNames. It offers one method parse(java.lang.String) to read out the CodeSections in a given String. Attention! This Parser can not read out as much as desired for the CodeSection. For more information, read through the java-doc of the method parse. *************************************************************************************** ******** No more usage of this class is made so far.

    • Method Detail

      • parse

        public CodeSection parse(String entityName)
                  throws FileNotFoundException
        Parsing a SoMoX-created String to get the annotated CodeSection.
        Parameters:
        entityName - SoMoX generated entityName. If not, this leads to undefined behaviour.
        Returns:
        May return null, if the String contains no file-path CodeSection. Initialized with (file, firstOffset, file, secondOffset) OR (file, firstOffset, file, firstOffset) if there is no second Offset available. Anyway, the first "file" and the second "file" are the same!
        Throws:
        FileNotFoundException - When the file was not found at the given relative path.
